{"tid":809574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國男稱肯亞人「像猴子」　涉歧視被逐出境","createTime":"2018-09-07T09:38:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T11:24:44.000Z","uid":39464,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"77155f9de43f546964e114b06049f7cbe1893775","tid":809574,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T09:38:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180907/s00004/01745abfaa2b110c6d1835ec94e00fcc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180907%2Fs00004%2F01745abfaa2b110c6d1835ec94e00fcc.jpg&h=1d11116c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名在肯尼亞的中國男子發表種族歧視言論，稱所有肯尼亞人包括總統都像「猴子」，被當局逐出境。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，該名涉事劉姓男子（Liu Jiaqi）為肯尼亞一家電單車店店主，他的僱員月初上載影片，片中劉稱要將另一名肯尼亞職員解僱「只因他是肯尼亞人」，並說肯尼亞「很臭、人民很窮、且又黑又愚蠢」，劉繼續攻擊肯尼亞人稱「他們都像猴子，包括總統甘耶達（Uhuru Kenyatta）」。當拍片的員工反問他為何仍留在肯尼亞時，劉說「錢很重要」，自己留在當地只為賺錢。<br />\n<br />\n肯尼亞警方在這影片上載後數小時將他拘捕，當局其後吊銷他的工作證並逐其出境。<br />\n<br />\n中國大使館發言人表示，劉已因其言論被公司處分，他亦已向該名肯尼亞同事道歉。發言人強調，劉的行為屬個別例子，並不代表大部分中國人。<br />\n<br />\n有網民贊成將劉驅逐出境，指若在非洲的中國人都是如此嘴臉，該把他們全都趕走，又有網民批評肯尼亞政府對中國政府有所顧忌，而容忍中國人的歧視行為。<br />\n<br />\n近年中國政府於肯尼亞大量投資，現時約有1萬名中國人居住於東非國家。肯尼亞之前亦有發生同類歧視事件，一名中國裔餐廳東主拒絕非洲裔顧客入內晚餐，引起當地極大反響，他後來被控無牌賣酒及餐廳衛生情況不合標準。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180907/s00004/1536311665367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180907%2Fs00004%2F1536311665367&d=y3Nr2Xfmn7RCtyCHc53wQQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=fe37abb5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180907%2Fs00004%2F1536311665367&h=9053de7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180907/s00004/1536311665367</a>"},{"pid":"913294976237b2cb72a773c2b02b9bca6e9813e3","tid":809574,"uid":197196,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T09:42:33.000Z","msg":"大家都是猴子 不用分那麼細"},{"pid":"5c10374aae8289a0c1642444b22a511a1788744a","tid":809574,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T09:46:11.000Z","msg":"連登仔撐邊面？"},{"pid":"5f06b870c326c37ac3558b2c54bfed466b04cf25","tid":809574,"uid":128568,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T09:47:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">他的僱員月初上載影片</span><br />\n<br />\n醒目仔,食埋佢間鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a4e6db38116663c8e493d9aba9533f6bc85d5b8","tid":809574,"uid":172485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T09:50:30.000Z","msg":"中國人都臭啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc1b50de2c8076183954235a27e55f0cdf6e0c92","tid":809574,"uid":127988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T10:00:38.000Z","msg":"肯亞人識聽支那語咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1f5861a39ee5f30613c9cc34c4909559f869697","tid":809574,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc1b50de2c8076183954235a27e55f0cdf6e0c92","tid":809574,"uid":127988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T10:00:38.000Z","msg":"肯亞人識聽支那語咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T10:03:56.000Z","msg":"條片係英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2dc08233d360a714d48f00e2b059cb3b47ccabd","tid":809574,"uid":171800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T10:03:58.000Z","msg":"中國幾時逐香港出境"},{"pid":"4864aaed2c87a1ce0ed2cd78f30628e90027d58f","tid":809574,"uid":127988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1f5861a39ee5f30613c9cc34c4909559f869697","tid":809574,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc1b50de2c8076183954235a27e55f0cdf6e0c92","tid":809574,"uid":127988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T10:00:38.000Z"